{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/2016-09-06-vault/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p><strong><em>Vault is a local password manager, a simple app with a minimal style.</em></strong></p>\n<div class=\"yt-video\">\n<iframe width=\"420\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/uHYALIsX7SY\">\n</iframe>\n</div>\n<!-- Check out the [trailer](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uHYALIsX7SY) -->\n<h1>Why use Vault?</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>◉ With Vault you have to remember only 1 password.</li>\n<li>◉ All the data is encrypted and saved only on your computer.</li>\n<li>◉ Vault doesn't require internet connection.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"/assets/img/projects/vault/2.jpg\" alt=\"Vault 1\">\n<img src=\"/assets/img/projects/vault/3.jpg\" alt=\"Vault 2\"></p>\n<h1>Download</h1>\n<iframe class=\"itch\" frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://itch.io/embed/89456?border_width=0&amp;fg_color=333&amp;link_color=ff4858\" width=\"550\" height=\"165\"></iframe>","frontmatter":{"title":"Vault - Password Manager","date":"September 6, 2016"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/2016-09-06-vault/"}}}